body:
**Thaumic Tweaks** is a mod that fixes some issues present in Thaumcraft and allows you to tweak some of it's aspects. (Vis Crystals and how they generate in the world, currently)

**Features**:
- Options for disabling crystal generation in certain biomes and dimensions (including specific crystal types, like Fire/Ignis Crystals);
- Options for tweaking the maximum and minimum height that crystals can spawn in;
- A new optional model for the Vis Crystals that more closely resembles the item sprites;
- Fixes shift clicking the slots in the Research Table not transfering the items to the player's inventory


If you want to mess with the other ores Thaumcraft adds I reccomend disabling their generation in Thaumcraft's config file and using [CoFH World](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/cofh-world) to generate them instead.
In case you're wondering, no, you can't replicate Thaumcraft's crystal generation using CoFH World, hence why I made this mod.
